    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、{user}さん\nうちとデートしませんか？",
      "startTime": 3.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "げほっ、ごほっ！！　……な、なんなんだ、いきなり\nそんなこと、出来る訳ないだろう",
      "startTime": 8.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ぐすん。いけずやわぁ、うちが勇気出して誘ったのに\nそこまで嫌がらんでもええやん",
      "startTime": 17.2943082809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、嫌とかそういうことじゃなくてだな\nマネージャーがそんな真似する訳にはいかないだろう",
      "startTime": 24.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、{user}さんは\n相変わらず真面目やね",
      "startTime": 29.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちは、アイドルとマネージャーの禁断の恋でも\n全然かまへんけどなぁ",
      "startTime": 36.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、冗談はこれくらいにしておいて\n実は今度、うちらの高校で学園祭があるんです",
      "startTime": 42.1239229519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんも観に来てくれませんか？\n瑠依ちゃんと一緒に、ミュージカルをやる予定なんよ",
      "startTime": 50.0572562853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……そういうことか、びっくりした\nでもそういうのって、ご両親が行くものじゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 58.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_14_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "それが学園祭の日に、お父さんもお母さんも\n仕事が入って、来られへんねん",
      "startTime": 66.151043256,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}